====================

**Government of Canada Tender Announcement**

### Notice Title

E60HL-230020/F - Diesel Fuel, Automotive Gasoline, and Heating Fuel

### Tender Number

WS4006758308

### Tender Status

This tender has expired and is no longer accepting submissions.

### Summary

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) is issuing a Request for Standing Offers (RFSO) for the supply of diesel fuel, automotive gasoline, and heating fuel oil. The RFSO cancels and supersedes previous RFSO notifications as indicated in the tender description.

### Description

The RFSO is for the establishment of National Master Standing Offers (NMSO) for diesel fuel, automotive gasoline, and heating fuel oil, in accordance with Canadian General Standards Board standards, as applicable. Deliveries will be made to various locations in Canada on an as-and-when-requested basis from May 30, 2024, to August 31, 2025.

### Requirements

- **Diesel Fuel**: 15101505
- **Automotive Gasoline**: 15101506
- **Diesel Fuel Off Road**: 15101513
- **Heating Fuel Oil**: 15101701
- **Biodiesel**: 15101801
- **Ethanol**: 15101802
- **Fuel Oil**: 83101602

### Termination of Previous RFSOs

This RFSO cancels and supersedes the following previous RFSOs:

- E60HL-230020/A (DOC4006944752) dated May 12, 2023, with a closing date of July 19, 2023.
- E60HL-230020/B (DOC4132763310) dated August 4, 2023, with a closing date of August 23, 2023.
- E60HL-230020/D (DOC4365086700) dated December 22, 2023, with a closing date of January 25, 2024.
- E60HL-230020/E (DOC4496135502) dated March 20, 2024, with a closing date of April 15, 2024.
